Class Messages

java.lang.Object
models.Messages
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Messages>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Enquiries, Suggestions
public class Messages extends Object implements Comparable<Messages>
This class represents a message with various attributes such as text, associated camp, index, sender, and status. It also provides functionalities for message comparison and equality checks.
